  "ai_usage": "Use to make a CTA or 'most popular' card stand out on AI/dev/SaaS sites. Put a rotating conic-gradient on a wrapper, then mask its center so only a ring shows (border); duplicate it blurred underneath for glow. Animate the angle via an @property <angle> custom property for a smooth spin. Keep the inner button accessible and pause under prefers-reduced-motion.",
  "path": "effects/buttons/gradient-border-glow.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Animated Gradient Border</title>\n  <script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n  {\n    \"id\": \"gradient-border-glow\",\n    \"title\": \"Animated Gradient Border\",\n    \"summary\": \"A button (or card) wrapped in a conic gradient border that rotates, with a soft matching glow.\",\n    \"description\": \"A rotating conic-gradient sits behind the element and is revealed only as a ring via a masked inset, so the border appears to spin. A blurred copy underneath adds a glow. Popular on AI/dev product CTAs and pricing 'featured' cards.\",\n    \"theme\": \"buttons\",\n    \"categories\": [\"button\", \"border\", \"animation\"],\n    \"tags\": [\"gradient-border\", \"conic\", \"glow\", \"animated\", \"ai\", \"2026-trend\"],\n    \"tech\": [\"css\"],\n    \"era\": \"2020s\",\n    \"difficulty\": \"intermediate\",\n    \"dependencies\": [],\n    \"browser_support\": \"Uses @property for smooth angle animation (Chromium/Safari/FF current); degrades to a static gradient where unsupported.\",\n    \"performance_notes\": \"One animated custom property driving a conic-gradient + a blurred glow layer. Pause on reduced-motion.\",\n    \"accessibility_notes\": \"Decorative border; keep the inner element a real button with focus-visible and adequate contrast.\",\n    \"customization\": [\n      { \"name\": \"--g1/--g2/--g3\", \"description\": \"Gradient stops\", \"default\": \"violet/teal/pink\" },\n      { \"name\": \"--speed\", \"description\": \"Rotation duration\", \"default\": \"4s\" }\n    ],\n    \"variations\": [\"Apply to pricing 'featured' cards\", \"Two-color sweep\", \"Reveal the spin only on hover\"],\n    \"related\": [\"magnetic-button\", \"neon-glow\", \"gradient-text\"],\n    \"ai_usage\": \"Use to make a CTA or 'most popular' card stand out on AI/dev/SaaS sites. Put a rotating conic-gradient on a wrapper, then mask its center so only a ring shows (border); duplicate it blurred underneath for glow. Animate the angle via an @property <angle> custom property for a smooth spin. Keep the inner button accessible and pause under prefers-reduced-motion.\"\n  }\n  </script>\n  <style>\n    @property --ang{syntax:'<angle>';inherits:false;initial-value:0deg}\n    :root{--g1:#7c5cff;--g2:#2dd4bf;--g3:#ff6ec7;--speed:4s;}\n    html,body{height:100%;margin:0}\n    body{display:grid;place-items:center;background:#0b0d12;font-family:system-ui,sans-serif}\n    .wrap{position:relative;padding:2px;border-radius:16px;isolation:isolate}\n    .wrap::before,.wrap::after{content:\"\";position:absolute;inset:0;border-radius:inherit;\n      background:conic-gradient(from var(--ang),var(--g1),var(--g2),var(--g3),var(--g1));\n      animation:spin var(--speed) linear infinite}\n    .wrap::after{filter:blur(14px);opacity:.7;z-index:-1}\n    .glow-btn{position:relative;border:none;cursor:pointer;background:#11131b;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;\n      padding:.95rem 2rem;border-radius:14px}\n    .glow-btn:focus-visible{outline:3px solid var(--g2);outline-offset:4px}\n    @keyframes spin{to{--ang:360deg}}\n    @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.wrap::before,.wrap::after{animation:none}}\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"wrap\"><button class=\"glow-btn\">✦ Generate with AI</button></div>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
